<item>
            <title>[LU-11377] setattr/setxattr don&apos;t need to set security irrelevant attrs/xattrs to shards</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11377</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently setattr/setxattr will set all attr/xattr on all shards for directory, if they are irrelevant to security, it&apos;s not necessary because client will merge attributes from master object and all shards, and xattr is obtained from master object. As a side effect, doing this will turn many operations into distributed operations, e.g. close will update atime, which makes system slow.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
